        <Parent_String>microphones [300266322], audio equipment [300257199], equipment for transmitting and reproducing sound [300257019], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
